    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This slender vial appears to hold clean, clear water with a faintly fruity scent. Drinking a *ration tonic* magically nourishes you with the equivalent of a day's worth of food and water. The tonic has a subtle, pleasant taste, its particulars chosen when the potion is crafted.",
